 5. On _Camper Vantiquities_, which song is the backwards song
    (originally)?

    The backwards song on _Camper Vantiquities_ is called "Om Eye",
    because the backwards lyrics sound like:

     Om Eye Sweet Isthmus, we are one
     Om Eye Sweet Isthmus, we are two

    The song that was reversed to make this song (with re-recorded
    bass and drums) is ``I Don't See You'', from _Telephone Free
    Landslide Victory_.

