 7. Who are the people in the pictures on the album covers?

    In the picture on the inside of the booklet to the German _II &
    III & Plus_ CD, from left to right are pictured Victor
    Krummenacher, Jonathan Segel, Chris Pedersen, (perhaps) Chris
    Molla, and David Lowery.

    On the reverse of the booklet in the Monks of Doom's _Forgery_,
    pictured are Greg Lisher, Chris Pedersen, David Immergluck, and
    Victor Krummenacher. In the booklet to _Meridian_ the pictures
    feature David, Victor, Greg, and finally Chris. In the picture in
    _Cosmodemonic Telegraph Company_ it's David, Chris, Victor, and
    Greg. And in _Breakfast on the Beach of Deception_ it's Greg,
    Victor, David, and Chris.

    On _Vampire Can Mating Oven_ it goes (from left to right) Jonathan
    Segel, Greg Lisher, Anthony Guess (drummer on the first record),
    David Lowery, Victor Krummenacher. Note that the same picture was
    used on the cover of _Camper Vantiquities_.

